relatedBlades.title: Play Pickleball with Cloudflare
relatedBlades.copy:
Visionary Bill Gates foresaw this over 50 years ago when he began playing, and loving, a newly created sport with a ridiculous name. Today the rest of us are catching up with him...and PICKLEBALL is the fastest growing sport in North America! 

Please join Cloudflare to connect with your peers to play __pickleball at the Bay Club in Burlingame on August 24th from 3:00PM-6:00PM PT.__ 

This event is great for all levels, even if you've never played before. We've hired a professional pickleball instructor to teach all of us how to play pickleball.  You'll get to play with your local peers and our team will be on hand to tell you everything about how we're here for your cyber security needs. We'll finish off with a networking reception with food, drinks and plenty of opportunities to connect with your local peers. 

__Event Details:__</br>
Date: Thursday, August 24, 2023</br> 
Time: 3:00PM - 6:00PM PT</br> 
Location: Bay Club Broadway Tennis & Pickleball, 60 Edwards Court, Burlingame, CA 94010</br> 

__Agenda:__ </br>
3:00 - 3:30 Welcome and registration</br>
3:30 - 4:00 Intro to pickleball clinic</br>
4:00 - 5:00 Pickleball shuffle play</br>
5:00 - 6:00 Networking with food and drinks</br> 

<sub>Please note, we have space for a limited number of players. Your spot is not confirmed until you receive official confirmation.</sub>
